OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1780409469
OL,3,CTeenager charged with murdering boy,
OL,4,C15, at house party
OL,6,FA teenager has been charged with
OL,7,Fmurdering a 15-year-old boy who was
OL,8,Ffatally stabbed after a fight spilled
OL,9,Fout of a house party in north-east
OL,10,FLondon.
OL,12,FMetropolitan Police officers were
OL,13,Fcalled to reports of a large
OL,14,Fgathering, disorder and people with
OL,15,Fmachetes on Towpath Walk, Hackney, at
OL,16,F7.17pm on Monday.
OL,18,FBrayan David Saldarriaga, 15, was
OL,19,Ffound with stab wounds in adjacent
OL,20,FPoplar Close, Hackney.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
