OL,3,CTeenager charged with murdering boy,
OL,4,C15, at house party
OL,6,FLondon Ambulance Service and Air
OL,7,FAmbulance Service also attended but
OL,8,FBrayan, from Haringey, north London,
OL,9,Fwas pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,11,FA 16-year-old, who cannot be named
OL,12,Fbecause of his age, will appear at
OL,13,FThames Magistrates' Court on Saturday.
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector Lucie Card,
OL,16,Fleading the investigation, said
OL,17,Fpreviously: "Our thoughts remain with
OL,18,FBrayan's loved ones following this
OL,19,Ftragic incident.
OL,26,@yD@MOU
