OL,3,CTeenager charged with murdering boy,
OL,4,C15, at house party
OL,6,F"They have asked for privacy as they
OL,7,Fcome to terms with Brayan's death and
OL,8,Fwe ask that their wishes are
OL,9,Frespected."
OL,11,FThe detective added: "We know there
OL,12,Fwere a significant number of people
OL,13,Fwho recorded the large gathering and
OL,14,Fthe incident on their mobile phone.
OL,16,F"I would urge anyone who witnessed
OL,17,Fwhat happened or who has footage of
OL,18,Fthe incident to come forward to police
OL,19,F` your information could be vital."
